      "ja": "チェスターはどこですか？",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Chester is next to the box.",
      "zh": "Chester 在盒子旁邊。",
      "ja": "チェスターは箱の隣にいます。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's next to it.",
      "zh": "他在旁邊。",
